{"image_id": "SBAC_2006_page_24", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "Table of Contents", "bbox": [37.5, 90.8, 206.4, 119.6]}, {"text": "PART II", "bbox": [37.5, 143.2, 125.9, 172.3]}, {"text": "Our Class A common stock is traded under the symbol “SBAC” on The NASDAQ Global Select Market. The following table presents", "bbox": [85.5, 232.2, 1212.7, 259.8]}, {"text": "the high and low sales price for the Class A common stock for the periods indicated:", "bbox": [37.5, 255.4, 752.2, 283.1]}, {"text": "As of February 26, 2007, there were 152 record holders of our Class A common stock.", "bbox": [85.5, 535.7, 818.2, 563.3]}, {"text": "Dividends", "bbox": [37.5, 586.7, 137.2, 615.8]}, {"text": "We have never paid a dividend on any class of common stock and anticipate that we will retain future earnings, if any, to fund the", "bbox": [85.5, 619.2, 1173.7, 646.8]}, {"text": "development and growth of our business. Consequently, we do not anticipate paying cash dividends on our common stock in the foreseeable", "bbox": [37.5, 642.2, 1213.7, 669.8]}, {"text": "future. In addition, we are restricted under our Initial CMBS Certificates, Additional CMBS Certificates and our senior credit facility from", "bbox": [37.5, 665.4, 1197.4, 693.1]}, {"text": "paying dividends or making distributions and repurchasing, redeeming or otherwise acquiring any shares of common stock except under certain", "bbox": [37.5, 688.4, 1240.7, 716.1]}, {"text": "circumstances.", "bbox": [37.5, 711.4, 171.2, 739.1]}, {"text": "Equity Compensation Plan Information", "bbox": [37.5, 762.7, 401.7, 791.8]}, {"text": "The following table gives information about our common stock that may be issued upon the exercise of options, warrants, and rights", "bbox": [85.5, 795.2, 1194.7, 822.8]}, {"text": "under all existing equity compensation plans as of December 31, 2006:", "bbox": [37.5, 818.2, 639.9, 845.8]}, {"text": "21", "bbox": [627.0, 1148.4, 652.9, 1176.1]}, {"text": "ITEM 5.", "bbox": [37.5, 177.